OL,1,D]S737{kkkc5FMinister urges people to be
OL,2,D]S555{jjj25F'sensible' over pay        
OL,3,D]Suuu{rrzq5F                           
OL,4,T#######################################
OL,5, Scotland's employment minister has     
OL,6, urged people to be "sensible" when     
OL,7, asking for pay rises.                  
OL,9,FRichard Lochhead acknowledged that many
OL,10,Fpeople were facing "huge pressure" as  
OL,11,Finflation hits 9%, a 40-year high.     
OL,13,FBut he said the country was in a       
OL,14,F"precarious position" and workers      
OL,15,Fshould ask for "affordable" wage       
OL,16,Fincreases.                             
OL,18,FBoth Aslef and the RMT have rejected a 
OL,19,F2.2% offer from the recently           
OL,20,Fnationalised train operator ScotRail.  
